data.description: Ask about the potentially assumable VA Mortgage.  Prairie Creek is a beautiful highly sought after community.  Fabulous community with 5-10 acre large lots.  Peaceful horse area with great riding trails.  This amazing property has its own private lake.  Property has an abundance of palm trees and fruit trees.  If you are looking for a peaceful quiet wide open property, look no further.  A feature that is hard to find is a private courtyard in the front of the house.  This is ideal for gardening, or just sitting out and enjoying your peaceful oasis.  In the back of the house there is a pool and spa that are covered by a lanai.  There are some minor damage to the pool area from Ian.  Priced to sell, now is the time to come see it, and place your offer.
